    • verifySplitPointScenario

      private void verifySplitPointScenario(int splitPointAfter, boolean shouldSplitStripe, float splitRatioToVerify, int... sizes) throws Exception
      Verifies scenario for finding a split point.
      Parameters:
      splitPointAfter - Stripe to expect the split point at/after.
      shouldSplitStripe - If true, the split point is expected in the middle of the above stripe; if false, should be at the end.
      splitRatioToVerify - Maximum split imbalance ratio.
      sizes - Stripe sizes.
      Throws:
      Exception
